parameters: Zerachiel: Oh my... an ambush, huh.

Zerachiel: But can you stop me all by
yourself?

Captain: Young lady, it would be best
for you to turn back quietly.

Zerachiel: Sorry, but it's not going to
go that way.

Zerachiel: Because I have a reason to
fight too.

Captain: Well then, I have no choice...
until I capture you here...!

Zerachiel: Let's settle this and see
who's stronger.

Captain: To be defeated by a little
girl... I underestimated you...!

Zerachiel: Uncle, is it already over?
This isn't exciting at all~!

Zerachiel: Well then... it's punishment
time, isn't it?

Female Voice: It's you who will be
punished.
Lady Saint: Oh my, are you the intruder?

Zerachiel: Ahaha, if I say it's
different~?

Lady Saint: If you quietly leave the
temple, you can avoid getting into
trouble.

Zerachiel: That's a cruel joke~. I can't
abandon my captured comrades.

Lady Saint: So that means...? You don't
intend to quietly turn back, do you?

Lady Saint: Oh my, you're such a
helpless child...

Lady Saint: Let me show you the power of
a saint.

Zerachiel: M-My strength... I can't
muster it... Why...

Lady Saint: There have been countless
angels like you who aimed for my life.

Lady Saint: The power of angels is
formidable. However...

Lady Saint: If you take precautions,
it's like dealing with a baby.

Zerachiel: What... have you done to
me...
Lady Saint: It's a curse of weakness.

Lady Saint: Your power has been lost due
to a curse.

Lady Saint: Your power won't return
anymore.

Lady Saint: Regret your audacity in
rampaging through the temple.

Zerachiel: My magical power... it has
all been drained...

Zerachiel: I can't lose like this...
kuuhh...!
Captain: Give up. Resistance is futile.

Zerachiel: Once my power returns, you
all...!

Lady Saint: It's unfortunate, but it
won't be that way.

Lady Saint: From now on, you will lose
everything.

Lady Saint: Take this girl to the
torture chamber.

Captain: In the torture chamber, make
sure those young ones give her plenty of
love and affection.
